  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nAfter unblocking a user it is not possible to send them messages\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Have a 1 to 1 chat with two users\r\n2. User 1 blocks user 2\r\n3. User 1 unblocks user 2\r\n4. User 1 can now receive messages from user 2 but not send them.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nAfter unblocking, both users can message each other.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/50769329/186411216-2cd55951-47a5-4e15-803b-dadd3999e7d4.mp4\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: https://ci.status.im/job/status-desktop/job/platforms/job/macos/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/pkg/StatusIm-Desktop-220824-111243-1c7719.dmg\r\n- Operating System: Mac\r\n\r\n",
